Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.00,English,,0,0,0,,In the name of Allāh, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.00,Arabic,,0,0,0,,ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ
