Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.00,English,,0,0,0,,[All] praise is [due] to Allāh, Lord of the worlds -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.00,Arabic,,0,0,0,,ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ
